quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,10,"Quluubtooda waxaa ah cudur (shaki, nifaaq, kibir, iwm), markaasuu Alle u kordhiyey cudur. Waxayna leeyihiin cadaab xanuun badan waxay been sheegi jireen darteed."
  2,11,"Marka lagu yidhaahdo: Ha fasaadanina (hallaynina) arlada, Waxay yidhaahdaan: Waxaanu nahay uun wax hagaajiyaal."
  2,12,"Ogaada, hubaal, Waa iyaga kuwa wax bi’iska ahi ee wax halleeya, mase ay dareensana."